    <briefdescription>
<para>TEE version. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Identifies the TEE implementation,<ref refid="structtee__version__info_1aaf74a1ff5fb899a0675724669a7d7e36" kindref="member">impl_id</ref> is one of TEE_IMPL_ID_* above. <ref refid="structtee__version__info_1a6cbf12676e5cfc1bdf4221a8188bf055" kindref="member">impl_caps</ref> is implementation specific, for example TEE_OPTEE_CAP_* is valid when <ref refid="structtee__version__info_1aaf74a1ff5fb899a0675724669a7d7e36" kindref="member">impl_id</ref> == TEE_IMPL_ID_OPTEE. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
